cretary]] [[Thomas Modly]], after a letter of his complaint over infections related to the [[2019\u201320 coronavirus pandemic]] was leaked.<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.bbc.com/news/world-us-canada-52145230|title=US Navy removes captain who raised virus alarm|date=2020-04-03|work=BBC News|access-date=2020-04-03|language=en-GB}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.cnn.com/2020/04/02/politics/uss-roosevelt-commander-relieved/index.html|title=Commander of aircraft carrier hit by coronavirus removed for 'poor judgment' after sounding alarm|last=CNN|first=Ryan Browne, Zachary Cohen and Jamie Crawford|website=CNN|access-date=2020-04-03}}</ref>\n\n== Honors, awards, and decorations ==\n{| style=\"margin-left:auto; margin-right:auto;\"\n|-\n|colspan=\"3\" |[[File:Naval Aviator Badge.jpg|220px|center]]\n|-\n|{{Ribbon devices|number=1|type=award-star|ribbon=Legion of Merit ribbon.svg|width=106}}\n|{{Ribbon devices|number=5|type=award-oak|ribbon=Defense Meritorious Service Medal ribbon.svg|width=106}}\n|{{Ribbon devices|number=0|type=award-oak|ribbon=Meritorious Service Medal ribbon.svg|width=106}}\n|-\n|{{ribbon devices|number=0|type=oak|ribbon=Air Medal ribbon.svg{{!}}border|width=106}}\n|{{ribbon devices|number=0|type=oak|ribbon=Joint Service Commendation ribbon.svg|width=106}}\n|{{ribbon devices|number=0|type=award-star|ribbon=Navy and Marine Corps Commendation ribbon.svg|width=106}}<span style=\"position:relative; top: 0px; left: -75px; display: inline-block; width: 0;\">[[File:1 golden star.svg|23px]]</span><span style=\"position:relative; top: 0px; left: -53px; display: inline-block; width: 0;\">[[File:1 golden star.svg|23px]]</span>\n|-\n|{{ribbon devices|number=1|type=award-star|ribbon=Navy and Marine Corps Achievement ribbon.svg|width=106}}\n|{{ribbon devices|number=0|type=service-star|ribbon=Navy Meritorious Unit Commendation ribbon.svg|width=106}}\n|{{ribbon devices|number=0|type=service-star|ribbon=Battle Effectiveness Award ribbon, 2nd award.svg|width=106}}\